72
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:34,990
Qin Lie!


73
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:36,090
Do it!


74
00:07:36,130 --> 00:07:37,360
We'll die no matter what,


75
00:07:37,470 --> 00:07:39,140
but we must take her with us!


76
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:42,370
Come on.


77
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:45,990
It's easy to kill, but it's the best
to break your heart!


78
00:07:46,110 --> 00:07:47,170
Come!


79
00:07:58,270 --> 00:07:59,270
Qin Lie.


80
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:02,390
How do you feel?


81
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,000
Are you happy?


82
00:08:06,830 --> 00:08:07,940
Set formation!


83
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,730
Soul Reaping Beast!


84
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:40,539
We have the same level of cultivation


85
