90
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:45,400
My daughter!


91
00:09:48,650 --> 00:09:51,380
Mother! Mother!


92
00:09:52,370 --> 00:09:53,580
The Saintess gave her order.


93
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:55,960
