95
00:09:57,930 --> 00:09:58,960
Yes!


96
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:11,360
Du Shao Yang!


97
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:12,940
What are you doing?


98
00:10:13,590 --> 00:10:15,930
I said I'm acting
on Saintess Song's orders.


99
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:18,840
The families in the Xingyun Pavilion
had perished.


100
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:21,780
Your father took the chance
and became the master.


101
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,070
In fear of losing his place,


102
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:26,620
he immediately joined
Song Ting Yu's forces.


103
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,820
I wanted to befriend you,


104
00:10:29,260 --> 00:10:30,850
but you had too many concerns.


105
00:10:32,630 --> 00:10:33,620
What a pity.


106
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:36,040
Song Ting Yu wants to kill us?


107
00:10:36,490 --> 00:10:38,500
We're unrelated to the Soul Reaping Beast.


108
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,140
Why are you killing us?


109
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,830
Song Ting Yu planned such a
formation just to hunt


110
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:49,860
the Soul Reaping Beast


111
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:52,630
and not caring about our lives.


112
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:55,880
It's obvious that


113
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:59,320
the Soul Reaping Beast was
not totally responsible


114
00:10:59,820 --> 00:11:01,670
for the 33 villages that were massacred.


115
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,800
Song Ting Yu must be responsible!


116
00:11:05,110 --> 00:11:07,020
So you want to keep us quiet from murder!


117
00:11:08,070 --> 00:11:09,090
Du Shao Yang!


118
00:11:09,180 --> 00:11:10,580
The Soul Reaping Beast


119
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,940
is really a tough enemy.


120
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:14,360
Why won't you let us out to fight?


121
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,270
With you?


122
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,980
Why waste our time with them?


123
00:11:19,070 --> 00:11:21,920
-Let's fight our way out, Qin Lie!
-That's right!


124
00:11:21,970 --> 00:11:26,290
Let's fight our way out!


125
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:27,650
Du Shao Yang.


126
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,420
Did you fight the Soul Reaping
Beast before?


127
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:31,480
I know you did.


128
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:33,020
So what?


129
00:11:33,410 --> 00:11:34,620
In the God Trapping Cave,


130
00:11:35,310 --> 00:11:36,320
and here.


131
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:39,270
I've fought the Soul Reaping Beast twice.


132
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:42,700
I know it better than you.


133
00:11:42,970 --> 00:11:44,920
It likes to disguise as others


134
00:11:45,820 --> 00:11:47,050
to hide itself.


135
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:49,030
It has great hatred


136
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:51,100
and great liking.


137
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,520
The hatred and liking


138
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:55,150
are both its weakness.


139
00:11:55,990 --> 00:11:58,630
Didn't you want to win
Song Ting Yu's favour?


140
00:11:59,070 --> 00:12:00,150
It hated


141
00:12:00,250 --> 00:12:01,790
me and Song Ting Yu the most.


142
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,630
It would be happy


143
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:05,210
to see me in pain.


144
00:12:06,490 --> 00:12:08,970
If it can witness our conflict,


145
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:10,630
it would show itself.


146
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:12,450
Let me out.


147
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:14,610
I'll fight the Soul Reaping Beast.


148
00:12:15,310 --> 00:12:16,580
You'll get the credit.


149
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:18,250
What do you think?


150
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:55,370
Gong Mu Lie?


151
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:03,790
Why didn't he look at you?


152
00:13:09,730 --> 00:13:11,400
How long did you love him?


153
00:13:11,990 --> 00:13:13,560
How long did you yearn for him?


154
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:16,720
You're standing in front of him now.


155
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:19,640
But why didn't he look at you?


156
00:13:20,990 --> 00:13:21,910
Why?


157
00:13:21,990 --> 00:13:23,590
Because he hates you.


158
00:13:24,250 --> 00:13:25,210
You're a liar!


159
00:13:25,270 --> 00:13:26,530
Song Ting Yu.


160
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:29,440
He would look at you with disgust.


161
00:13:31,310 --> 00:13:32,650
Are you afraid?


162
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:36,610
How would it feel to be hated


163
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:39,030
by your loved one?


164
00:13:40,210 --> 00:13:42,440
Do you dare to look into his eyes?


165
00:14:04,410 --> 00:14:05,350
You wretch!


166
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:17,960
-Aunt Hua is dead, Uncle Ling is dead.
-Qin Lie!


167
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,900
Everyone of the Ling family is dead!


168
00:14:19,990 --> 00:14:21,140
It's all your fault!


169
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:23,120
I'll kill you, Song Ting Yu!


170
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:26,330
How dare you, Qin Lie?


171
00:14:34,340 --> 00:14:35,480
It's him!


172
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:49,560
What a great fight!


173
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,770
You're not young anymore.


174
00:14:51,890 --> 00:14:53,640
Why are you acting like a child


175
00:14:53,730 --> 00:14:56,030
and showed yourself when we're fighting?


176
00:14:58,230 --> 00:14:59,490
How dare you be insolent?


177
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,260
It was for the plan.


178
00:15:01,350 --> 00:15:03,640
You did it on purpose!


179
00:15:03,830 --> 00:15:05,530
Why are you acting like a child too?


180
00:15:05,630 --> 00:15:06,900
Subdue it first!


181
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:19,970
Uncle Liang!


182
00:15:20,270 --> 00:15:22,690
Don't worry, we've planted our
men all over the place to


183
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:24,140
force it to the Silent Abyss.


184
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,860
-After it!
-After it!


185
00:15:31,990 --> 00:15:33,250
Silent Abyss?


186
00:15:54,590 --> 00:15:55,580
Follow up!


187
00:17:09,740 --> 00:17:12,430
[Silent Abyss]


188
00:17:10,930 --> 00:17:12,950
Saintess, it's in the Silent Abyss.


189
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:15,819
Let's go down.


190
00:17:15,950 --> 00:17:17,310
-Yes!
-Yes!


191
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:53,610
Why don't you attack?


192
00:17:54,250 --> 00:17:56,850
You can't use your illusion here, huh?


193
00:17:57,990 --> 00:18:00,440
Skilled masters had duelled here
ten thousand years ago


194
00:18:00,630 --> 00:18:03,370
and broke the balance of the
world with their might.


195
00:18:03,740 --> 00:18:06,940
Therefore, a strong Soul Dispersing
Barrier was cast here.


196
00:18:07,520 --> 00:18:10,550
Every illusion would lose its magic here.


197
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:16,530
The hunt on the snowing grounds,
Snow God Valley,


198
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:19,870
the Ling Borough and the Silent Abyss


199
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:23,260
are all your doings.


200
00:18:23,570 --> 00:18:25,020
You used countless lives


201
00:18:25,430 --> 00:18:27,400
as your trap just to kill me.


202
00:18:29,110 --> 00:18:30,920
Everyone said we're evil.


203
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:34,180
But the real evil is you, the humans!


204
00:18:34,270 --> 00:18:35,790
Xie Jing Xuan died because of you.


205
00:18:35,930 --> 00:18:37,690
I'll sacrifice you to appease her soul.


206
00:18:37,930 --> 00:18:38,920
Set formation!


207
00:18:56,950 --> 00:18:58,900
How would such thunder power affect me?


208
00:19:02,730 --> 00:19:04,360
Baji Fire Formation!


209
00:19:19,890 --> 00:19:21,480
You can't stand thunder and fire.


210
00:19:21,570 --> 00:19:23,050
You'll die today.


211
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,150
Saintess!


212
00:19:42,940 --> 00:19:45,760
You used the Ghost Fire Skull Formation
on yourself?


213
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:56,050
It levelled up.


214
00:19:56,140 --> 00:19:57,480
How could this be?


215
00:19:58,450 --> 00:20:00,590
So what with the Soul Dispersing Barrier?


216
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:03,090
I'm not restricted from any rules


217
00:20:03,420 --> 00:20:05,820
if I use my body as the medium
of the formation.


218
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:08,020
The Silent Abyss


219
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:10,490
will be your grave today.


220
00:20:11,230 --> 00:20:12,370
Die!


221
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:17,000
You should be the one to die!


222
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:18,430
Qin Lie!


223
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:19,880
Leave!


224
00:20:26,450 --> 00:20:27,530
Let's go, Saintess.


225
00:20:27,740 --> 00:20:28,830
Let's go!


226
00:20:35,320 --> 00:20:36,300
Let's go.


227
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:37,410
Let's go!


228
00:20:46,780 --> 00:20:48,190
The Thunder Jade.


229
00:20:48,550 --> 00:20:49,910
Qin Lie was here.


230
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:53,080
Saintess.


231
00:20:55,700 --> 00:20:57,340
Are you alright, Saintess?


232
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:53,490
Heavenly Thunder?


233
00:21:53,930 --> 00:21:55,110
Thunder of the Ninth Heaven?


234
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:56,740
Why is it here?


235
00:22:39,300 --> 00:22:40,300
Hua Yu Xin!


236
00:22:47,820 --> 00:22:48,970
Yu Shi.


237
00:23:39,790 --> 00:23:40,750
Yu Shi!


238
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:43,700
Yu Shi.


239
00:23:55,760 --> 00:24:01,030
[Lin Yu Shi enters the memory
from 10,000 years ago]


240
00:24:11,410 --> 00:24:12,870
In the beginning,


241
00:24:13,180 --> 00:24:15,600
the Realm of Ruined Souls
bore sacred stones


242
00:24:16,360 --> 00:24:19,340
with a crystal-like and
exquisite disposition.


243
00:24:20,430 --> 00:24:22,380
It can foresee everything in the world


244
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:24,930
and relates with promises.


245
00:24:26,030 --> 00:24:28,310
[The Mother of Earth and the
Child of the War God]


246
00:24:28,390 --> 00:24:29,590
[shouldn't fall in love.]


247
00:24:30,070 --> 00:24:31,570
[If made known to evil forces,]


248
00:24:31,950 --> 00:24:33,860
[they won't come to a good end


249
00:24:34,080 --> 00:24:35,620
[before they could be together.]


250
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:37,510
[But now,]


251
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:40,370
[you've developed feelings
for each other.]


252
00:24:40,460 --> 00:24:43,700
[Chong Ming]


253
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:42,530
Do you choose to fight each other


254
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:44,420
or forget each other?


255
00:24:44,950 --> 00:24:46,440
[You may decide on your own.]


256
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:14,650
The Soul Dispersing Barrier was broken.


257
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:17,370
I never thought that


258
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:20,370
the Thunder of the Ninth Heaven
would be so powerful.


259
00:25:21,110 --> 00:25:23,180
How can Qin Lie summon
the heavenly thunder


260
00:25:23,360 --> 00:25:25,730
and break the rules of the
heaven and earth?


261
00:25:29,230 --> 00:25:31,060
The Soul Reaping Beast is dead.


262
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:33,210
The Thunderbolt subdues evil.


263
00:25:33,600 --> 00:25:35,110
All evil in the world


264
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:37,660
can never escape the wrath
of the Thunderbolt.


265
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:40,610
The Soul Reaping Beast
has been eliminated.


266
00:25:42,350 --> 00:25:43,380
What about Qin Lie?


267
00:25:43,540 --> 00:25:45,890
He must've perished with it.


268
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:52,130
Du Shao Yang, who exactly is this


269
00:25:52,490 --> 00:25:54,250
Qin Lie?


270
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:57,020
He's just an average cultivator
from the Ling family.


271
00:25:58,000 --> 00:26:00,320
But I didn't know why he was able to


272
00:26:01,110 --> 00:26:02,470
summon the Thunderbolt.


273
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:11,760
I don't want word the hunt to get out.


274
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,340
Do you understand?


275
00:26:15,280 --> 00:26:16,240
Yes.


276
00:26:16,420 --> 00:26:18,660
The Ling Borough will be destroyed.


277
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:21,520
If you accomplish the mission,


278
00:26:21,760 --> 00:26:25,190
I'll name your father as the master
of the Xingyun Pavilion.


279
00:26:29,240 --> 00:26:30,370
Thank you, Saintess.


280
00:26:35,250 --> 00:26:37,850
General Pu Jiao at your service, Saintess.


